file.name: path_parameter.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: V1
  version: 0.1.0
servers:
  - url: "{server}:{port}/v1"
    variables:
      server:
        default: http://localhost
      port:
        default: "9090"
paths:
  /pet/{petId}:
    get:
      operationId: "operation_get_/pet/{petId}"
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int64
      responses:
        "202":
          description: Accepted
  /{pet-id}:
    get:
      operationId: "operation_get_/{pet-id}"
      parameters:
        - name: pet-id
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        "202":
          description: Accepted
  /pets/{petId}/owner/{owner-id}:
    get:
      operationId: "operation_get_/pets/{petId}/owner/{owner-id}"
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: owner-id
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "202":
          description: Accepted
components: {}
